aFmHA Forms 194430, ``Identity of Interest (IOI) Disclosure Certificate,'' and FmHA 194431,
``Identity of Interest (IOI) Qualification Form,'' (available in any FmHA Servicing office) will be completed and
submitted as part of the management plan. Management agents will sign either form as ``applicant.'' 
bThe initial disclosure shall be in effect for a period of 3 years and renewed every 3 years thereafter, except
if there are any changes in the business practices of the applicant/borrower and/or management entity during the
interim years that include identity of interest concerns, the entity must file amended Forms FmHA 194430 and
FmHA 194431. 
cThe forms provide notification to the entities of the penalty, under law, for erroneously certifying to
the statements contained therein. 


